<p>
<lb n="1"/>śrī śākē rāmavahnitriśaśini vimalē jyēṣṭamāsēṁduvārē
<lb n="2"/>hastarkṣē vriddhiyōgē paśupatidivasē muktadēśēṁdrabhāryā
<lb n="3"/>naṁgāṁbātrēyagōtrā sahajaniranagha <gap reason="lost" quantity="2" unit="character"/> śaṁbhōrgurōḥ
<lb n="4"/>pūjāṁ puṣpairakārṣījjagati vijayatāṁ siṁhyaśailēśvarasya <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> sva
<lb n="5" break="no"/>sti śrī <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> śakavaruṣaṁbulu 1333 gunēṁṭi jyēṣṭa sukla 11 dasi sō
<lb n="6" break="no"/>mavarana kaḷēśvara muktināta Ana<unclear>śva</unclear>rācārya tripurāṁtaka
<lb n="7" break="no"/>AghōraĀcāryula vāṭhinaṁgama tanaku Iṣṭartthasidhigānu śrīnara
<lb n="8" break="no"/>siṁhyanādhuniki nityamunnu māpaṭi dupaAvasaramaṁdu [Ādi]ga
<lb n="9" break="no"/>nu tirutōmāla Okaṭi samarppiṁcenu Iṁdali kanumadēvarayani
<lb n="10"/>kaṁcinayani <unclear>pra</unclear>tā<unclear>ṁ</unclear> ĀraI veṁḍiṭaṁkalu 5 peṭi vāśinayakana pasadaṁ
<lb n="11" break="no"/>lō kuṁ<unclear>ka</unclear> ṭavupaṭi peṭitimi sīyamahāsēnāpativāri sēta gōpā
<lb n="12" break="no"/>ḷanāyani variŪrigaṭuna puṣpavāṭika gaṭu 1 koni peṭitimi I mā
<lb n="13" break="no"/><unclear>la</unclear>tecci peṭa<unclear>nu</unclear> <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> ku Istimi I prasadaṁbu<note n="318-1">The continuation of this inscription is lost.</note>
